{"tid":2375121,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"第三波疫情市民最疲勞放棄抵抗 專家預言：2022年尾才可正常出遊","createTime":"2021-01-21T19:34:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-23T06:37:54.000Z","uid":29627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7340bd17e78b25afc562e7f3dbb12ecc1f7f64ce","tid":2375121,"uid":29627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T19:34:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210122/PASKOKUPNVBM5G3C4MMQPAJZMQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210122%2FPASKOKUPNVBM5G3C4MMQPAJZMQ%2F&d=CT6PJiTX903K6YLxhzu4TQjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=0301b3a9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210122%2FPASKOKUPNVBM5G3C4MMQPAJZMQ%2F&h=19382420\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210122/PASKOKUPNVBM5G3C4MMQPAJZMQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎疫情肆虐一年，由最初口罩供應緊絀，到分析疫情發展、防疫措施和疫苗等，都不乏民間專家頻頻講解，其中感染及傳染病專科醫生曾祈殷於03年沙士時開始接受專科訓練，未料17年後再次遇上大疫症，雖然已離開公院，但一直緊貼事態分析疫情。他直言自己也有「抗疫疲勞」，更預計要到2022年底，全球疫情才會真正受控，愛旅遊的港人才可重新出行。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf6bd60332a5258d8d62ceae7bae4057fb28e893","tid":2375121,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T19:39:09.000Z","msg":"有林鄭月娥唔疲勞先出奇<br />\n清零完又放病毒入境<br />\n最基本封關檢疫都搞到一篤屎咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/throw.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"574848656da0a98d7f44b1b7265b3e03c01f3038","tid":2375121,"uid":17545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T06:37:54.000Z","msg":"說好的疫苗呢？"}]}